"""duh v2 — macOS APFS-aware disk-usage database CLI.

Detects hardlinks AND APFS clones (via getattrlist ATTR_CMNEXT_CLONEID).
macOS-only. stdlib only.

v2 changes:
- parent_id replaces parent_path (compact adjacency-list schema)
- Default exclusions for regenerable trees (node_modules, .venv, etc.)
- Disk-safety monitor aborts scan if free space drops below threshold
- 256 MB query cache for analytical commands
- New `excluded` subcommand to show skipped subtrees
"""

